Lotka–Volterra Observation Dashboard

Compare real-world predator–prey population data with the theoretical Lotka–Volterra model.

What this dashboard will do

  • Fetch predator and prey population data from public APIs.
  • Visualize population changes over time.
  • Create predator vs. prey phase-plane diagrams.
  • Run and compare theoretical Lotka–Volterra simulations.

How to navigate

Use the navigation bar at the top to explore dashboard views.
